io.spine.server.outbus

Class OutputDispatcherRegistry<C extends io.spine.type.MessageClass,D extends MessageDispatcher<C,?,?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.server.bus.DispatcherRegistry<C,D>
      • io.spine.server.outbus.OutputDispatcherRegistry<C,D>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RejectionDispatcherRegistry

    @Internal
public class OutputDispatcherRegistry<C extends io.spine.type.MessageClass,D extends MessageDispatcher<C,?,?>>
extends DispatcherRegistry<C,D>
    A base registry of the dispatchers, responsible for dispatching the command output to the corresponding objects.

    The registries of this kind are managed by the descendants of CommandOutputBus.

    See Also:
    CommandOutputBus
